  "Set −5t² + 2t + 10 = 0. Using a = −5, b = 2, c = 10: t = (−2 ± √(4 + 200))/(−10) = (−2 ± √204)/(−10). √204 ≈ 14.28. Taking the positive root: t = (−2 − 14.28)/(−10) ≈ 1.6 seconds.": "设置-5t2+2t+10=0。使用 a =-5,b =2,c = 10 t = (-2 + + 200)/(- 10) = (-2 + + + 204)/(- 10) = (-2 + + + + 204)/(- 10) = (-2 + + + + 2t + + 10 = 0。使用正根 : t = (-2 - 14.28)/(- 10) = 1.6 秒。",
  "A firework is launched with height h = −16t² + 80t. An observer on a building at height 96 feet wants to know when the firework passes their level. Solve using the quadratic formula.": "发射的烟花高度为 h = − 16t2 + 80t。在96英尺高的一栋建筑上,观察者想知道烟花何时通过水平。使用二次公式解决。",
