  "Set −16t² + 80t = 96: −16t² + 80t − 96 = 0. Divide by −16: t² − 5t + 6 = 0. Using the formula: t = (5 ± √(25 − 24))/2 = (5 ± 1)/2. So t = 3 or t = 2. The firework passes 96 feet at 2 and 3 seconds.": "设定 - 16t2 + 80t = 96: - 16t2 + 80t = 96 = 0。除以 16: t2 - 5t + 6 = 0。使用公式: t = (5 + + + + 16t2 + 80t = 96 : - 16t2 + 80t + = 96 = 0。使用公式: t = (5 + + + + 24)/2 = (5 + 1)/2。 所以 t = 3 或 t = 2. 消防队在2秒和3秒内通过96英尺。",
  "A store models revenue as R = −3x² + 54x, where x is the price in dollars. At what prices is the revenue exactly $216?": "R = - 3x2 + 54x 的存储模型收入, 以美元计价 x 。 以什么价格计价的收入是 216 美元 ?",
