  "Set −3x² + 54x = 216: −3x² + 54x − 216 = 0. Divide by −3: x² − 18x + 72 = 0. Using the formula: x = (18 ± √(324 − 288))/2 = (18 ± 6)/2. So x = 12 or x = 6.": "设置 - 3x2 + 54x = 216: - 3x2 + 54x + 216 = 0。除以 3: x2 - 18x + 72 = 0。使用公式: x = (18 =   (324 - 288))/2 = (18  6)/2 = (2 = 6 = 6)。 所以 x = 12 或 x = 6。",
  "An engineer uses the equation 3x² − 12x + 9 = 0 to model stress points on a bridge. How many real solutions does this equation have, and what are they?": "工程师使用 3x2 - 12x + 9 = 0 等式来模拟桥上的压力点。 这个等式有多少真正的解决方案, 是什么?",
  "Two solutions: x = 1 and x = 3": "两种解决办法:x=1和x=3",
