  "A football is kicked and follows the path h = −4.9t² + 14.7t + 1, where h is meters and t is seconds. A goalpost crossbar is at h = 3.05 m. Using the quadratic formula, does the ball clear the crossbar at t = 0.15 seconds?": "足球被踢,并沿着 h =-4.9t2 + 14.7t + 1 路径前进,那里是米和秒。 目标柱十字栏在h = 3. 05米。 使用四方形公式, 球是否在 t = 0. 15 秒处清除十字栏?",
  "Yes, the ball is at about 3.1 m at t = 0.15 s, clearing the 3.05 m crossbar": "是,球在t = 0.15 秒时约3.1米处,清除3.05米横杆",
